00:23:48,226 --> 00:23:50,751
I realize you just called him
'cause you care.

267
00:23:51,897 --> 00:23:54,422
And I was wrong
to get angry at you.

268
00:23:56,201 --> 00:23:58,795
But you have to realize something.
I've been through

269
00:23:58,870 --> 00:24:01,805
