and a dozen different shrinks.

270
00:24:01,873 --> 00:24:04,467
And the only thing that I've found
is that it doesn't work.

271
00:24:07,379 --> 00:24:10,212
Come on. You can't be mad
at me forever.

272
00:24:10,282 --> 00:24:13,115
How about I ditch
my morning class

273
00:24:13,185 --> 00:24:15,847
and we go to Clark's
for breakfast?

274
00:25:02,367 --> 00:25:04,096
Don't call me.
I'm over this.

275
00:25:04,169 --> 00:25:05,568
Wait.

276
00:25:09,207 --> 00:25:10,674
Oh, Jesus.

277
00:25:14,045 --> 00:25:16,206
Oh my God.

278
00:25:20,452 --> 00:25:22,450
So how long do you need
the gymnasium for?

279
00:25:22,521 --> 00:25:25,183
Uh...
a few more weeks.

280
00:25:25,257 --> 00:25:27,623
Ryan.
I'll see you later.

281
00:25:29,227 --> 00:25:31,388
Hey, how's Creative Writing
coming along?

282
00:25:33,765 --> 00:25:36,325
Did you have
another nightmare?

283
00:25:36,401 --> 00:25:38,835
Yeah, but this time it was...
