284
00:25:38,904 --> 00:25:40,769
You know, it felt more real.

285
00:25:40,839 --> 00:25:42,807
Stronger.

286
00:25:42,874 --> 00:25:45,069
Why don't we step
into my office?

287
00:25:45,143 --> 00:25:46,974
All right.

288
00:25:49,481 --> 00:25:51,176
So how's your girlfriend?

289
00:25:51,249 --> 00:25:53,308
It's Rachel, right?

290
00:25:53,385 --> 00:25:55,910
