291
00:25:55,987 --> 00:26:00,219
Well, you know, you just got to give
these things some time.

292
00:26:00,292 --> 00:26:02,055
I guess.

293
00:26:20,445 --> 00:26:22,379
Everything all right?

294
00:26:24,516 --> 00:26:26,279
It's deja vu.

295
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:31,821
Some cultures believe
that deja vu

296
00:26:31,890 --> 00:26:34,484
