you're on the right path.

297
00:26:34,559 --> 00:26:36,584
Is that so?

298
00:26:36,661 --> 00:26:38,891
It could also be a hiccup
in your brain chemistry

299
00:26:38,964 --> 00:26:41,455
as you process new information
through a memory cell.

300
00:26:42,567 --> 00:26:44,967
So which one is it?

301
00:26:46,271 --> 00:26:49,468
- Why couldn't it be both?
- Both?

302
00:26:50,909 --> 00:26:54,345
Sure. Why couldn't the chemical
hiccups have a purpose?

303
00:26:54,412 --> 00:26:57,779
Everything does.
It's all part of the master plan.

304
00:26:57,849 --> 00:27:00,317
So what about
my nightmares?

305
00:27:00,385 --> 00:27:02,478
Are they also
part of the plan?

306
00:27:03,955 --> 00:27:07,391
Sure. Why not?
There's so much we don't know.

307
00:27:07,459 --> 00:27:10,257
It's called
the Butterfly Effect.

308
00:27:10,328 --> 00:27:13,627
Yeah, a flap of the wings

309
00:27:13,698 --> 00:27:16,599
on one side of the planet
can cause waves on the other.

310
00:27:18,670 --> 00:27:20,865
Something like that.

311
00:27:20,939 --> 00:27:23,032
Everything that ever happened
in history

312
00:27:23,108 --> 00:27:26,100
happened from a chain reaction
from previous events,

313
00:27:26,177 --> 00:27:29,010
which still continues
to this day.

314
00:27:29,080 --> 00:27:30,980
Our lives
are governed by it.

315
00:27:31,049 --> 00:27:32,983
You're a prime example.

316
00:27:33,051 --> 00:27:34,916
Did you choose to have
these nightmares?

317
00:27:34,986 --> 00:27:36,385
No.

318
00:27:36,454 --> 00:27:38,183
But I chose
not to have them.

319
00:27:40,625 --> 00:27:43,651
So how's that
working for you?

320
00:27:43,728 --> 00:27:46,526
Great.

321
00:27:46,598 --> 00:27:48,532
It's all about cause
and effect.

322
00:27:48,600 --> 00:27:52,161
We need to find out the cause that
effected you with these nightmares

323
00:27:52,237 --> 00:27:55,695
and see what we can do
to effect it to stop.

324
00:27:57,409 --> 00:28:00,344
You know, my sister wasn't the only one
that went missing that night.

325
00:28:00,412 --> 00:28:02,437
