the ultimate game.

335
00:28:25,970 --> 00:28:27,995
You ever heard of the game
Bloody Mary Worth?

336
00:28:30,475 --> 00:28:32,534
Well, my sister did.

337
00:28:32,610 --> 00:28:35,204
