pick up the phone and call her yourself.

346
00:29:54,225 --> 00:29:55,852
What is with her?

347
00:29:55,927 --> 00:29:58,760
She probably fell asleep
or something.

348
00:29:58,830 --> 00:30:01,264
Forget it.

349
00:30:01,332 --> 00:30:04,028
Girl is probably dead
to the world.

350
00:30:15,947 --> 00:30:17,642
So what's next?

351
00:30:17,715 --> 00:30:19,876
Hey, this might be cool.

352
00:30:19,951 --> 00:30:22,351
