the legendary game Mary Worth."

382
00:32:08,693 --> 00:32:10,820
Wow, look at the crazy icons.

383
00:32:13,431 --> 00:32:15,558
"17th-century Salem court,

384
00:32:15,633 --> 00:32:18,067
Mary Worth was sentenced
to death

385
00:32:18,136 --> 00:32:20,070
for the crimes
of witchcraft.

386
00:32:20,138 --> 00:32:23,733
On October 31st her sentence
was carried out.

387
00:32:23,808 --> 00:32:27,300
Mary had to endure
brutal beatings for hours

388
00:32:27,378 --> 00:32:30,939
as the townspeople tried
desperately to make her confess

389
00:32:31,015 --> 00:32:32,642
who her unborn child's
father was."

390
00:32:34,886 --> 00:32:37,446
Mary Worth,

391
00:32:37,522 --> 00:32:40,286
thou hast been granted
bountiful occasion

392
00:32:40,358 --> 00:32:44,055
to divulge the proper name
of thy bastard child.

393
00:32:44,128 --> 00:32:47,586
It yet be the opinion
of this court

394
00:32:47,665 --> 00:32:50,156
