419
00:35:23,554 --> 00:35:26,455
Fellow citizens,

420
00:35:26,524 --> 00:35:29,755
children of God,

421
00:35:29,827 --> 00:35:31,886
it is a hypocritical legacy

422
00:35:31,963 --> 00:35:34,227
we so-called
Puritans bear.

423
00:35:34,298 --> 00:35:37,563
For there is not
one amongst us

424
00:35:37,635 --> 00:35:39,330
without the stain of sin,

425
00:35:39,403 --> 00:35:41,633
not one who is blameless.

426
00:35:43,241 --> 00:35:46,142
Mankind be wretched
and culpable.

427
00:36:19,243 --> 00:36:21,768
"Now she's trapped
in the mirror

428
00:36:21,846 --> 00:36:23,279
and seeking vengeance,

429
00:36:23,347 --> 00:36:25,178
waiting for someone
to believe in her

430
00:36:25,249 --> 00:36:27,217
