to Mary's game.

433
00:36:31,756 --> 00:36:34,088
Several poor souls
wrote their names

434
00:36:34,158 --> 00:36:36,149
and those of their friends
onto a mirror

435
00:36:36,227 --> 00:36:38,923
and then, believing
in Mary, in short,

436
00:36:38,996 --> 00:36:42,193
